high_descs: Turn right, and go straight to the kitchen area, then to the fridge on the left.
Remove the dirty plate from the fridge.
Go towards the sink to the right of the fridge.
Wash the plate in the sink.
Turn around, take the first left and walk towards the wall, then right into the bedroom, walking around the bed towards the dresser.
Place the plate on the dresser between the controller and the bowl.
